---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Contact — Global Wealth Portfolio"
  description="Get in touch with the Global Wealth Portfolio team. We'd love to hear from you."
>
  <section class="container-page page-section pt-3xl pb-2xl max-w-3xl">
    <p class="text-caption-mono text-body mb-xs">Contact</p>
    <h1 class="text-display-lg mb-lg">We'd love to hear from you.</h1>
    <p class="text-body-md text-body mb-2xl">
      Have a question, feature request, or found a bug? Reach out &mdash; we
      read every message.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-2xl mb-3xl">
      <div class="card-soft p-lg">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-sm mb-sm">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"></path>
            <polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"></polyline>
          </svg>
          <h2 class="text-display-sm">Email</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-body-sm text-body mb-sm">General inquiries &amp; support:</p>
        <a href="mailto:hello@globalwealthfolio.com" class="text-body-md text-link hover:underline">hello@globalwealthfolio.com</a>
        <p class="text-body-sm text-body mt-md mb-sm">Privacy concerns:</p>
        <a href="mailto:privacy@globalwealthfolio.com" class="text-body-md text-link hover:underline">privacy@globalwealthfolio.com</a>
      </div>

      <div class="card-soft p-lg">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-sm mb-sm">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M12 .5C5.65.5.5 5.65.5 12c0 5.08 3.29 9.39 7.86 10.92.58.1.79-.25.79-.55 0-.27-.01-1-.02-1.95-3.2.69-3.87-1.54-3.87-1.54-.52-1.32-1.27-1.67-1.27-1.67-1.04-.71.08-.7.08-.7 1.15.08 1.76 1.18 1.76 1.18 1.02 1.75 2.68 1.24 3.34.95.1-.74.4-1.24.72-1.53-2.55-.29-5.24-1.27-5.24-5.66 0-1.25.45-2.27 1.18-3.07-.12-.29-.51-1.46.11-3.05 0 0 .96-.31 3.15 1.18.91-.25 1.89-.38 2.86-.38.97 0 1.95.13 2.86.38 2.18-1.49 3.15-1.18 3.15-1.18.62 1.59.23 2.76.11 3.05.74.8 1.18 1.82 1.18 3.07 0 4.4-2.69 5.36-5.25 5.65.41.35.78 1.05.78 2.12 0 1.53-.01 2.77-.01 3.14 0 .3.21.66.8.55C20.21 21.39 23.5 17.08 23.5 12 23.5 5.65 18.35.5 12 .5z"/>
          </svg>
          <h2 class="text-display-sm">GitHub</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-body-sm text-body mb-sm">Report bugs, request features, or contribute:</p>
        <a href="https://github.com/sourabh6303/globalwealthfolio" class="text-body-md text-link hover:underline break-all" rel="noopener" target="_blank">github.com/sourabh6303/globalwealthfolio</a>
      </div>

      <div class="card-soft p-lg">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-sm mb-sm">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
            <line x1="2" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12"></line>
            <path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"></path>
          </svg>
          <h2 class="text-display-sm">Web</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-body-sm text-body mb-sm">Documentation &amp; changelog:</p>
        <a href="/blog" class="text-body-md text-link hover:underline">/blog</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-display-md mt-2xl mb-md">Frequently asked</h2>
    <div class="space-y-sm">
      <div class="card-soft p-lg">
        <h3 class="text-display-sm mb-xs">Is Global Wealth Portfolio really free?</h3>
        <p class="text-body-sm text-body">Yes. Every feature is available without payment, account creation, or trial. We do not have paid tiers or premium features.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-soft p-lg">
        <h3 class="text-display-sm mb-xs">Do you store my data on your servers?</h3>
        <p class="text-body-sm text-body">No. All data stays in your browser's local storage. We do not have servers that store your portfolio, expenses, or any personal information.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-soft p-lg">
        <h3 class="text-display-sm mb-xs">How quickly do you respond?</h3>
        <p class="text-body-sm text-body">We aim to respond to email within 48 hours. For bugs and security issues, we typically respond much faster &mdash; often within a few hours.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
